metadata.title: 2 Pairs Safety Glasses Side Shields,Fits Medium to Large Eyeglasses Clear
features: HIGH QUALITY: Made of flexible softness TPU, comfort cushions allow custom facial fitting.
APPLY TO: Universal side shields that fit Medium to Large frames eyeglasses. Package 2 Pairs.
EASY TO INSTALL: Easy-on, easy-off, weaves through the glasses temple, no parts or tools required for installation.
COMFORTABLE: Use for visual comfort and productivity, To be used on metal frame safety eyewear where additional protection is needed.
ENVIRONMENTALLY: Environmentally friendly designed to absorb the energy of impact and protect your eyes to injuries from windblown particulates.
description: Material: Soft TPU material Color: Clear Lens thickness: 1-2 mm Size: approx. 50 * 45 * 20mm.
2 * Pairs Safety eye glasses side shields
The Safety Glasses Side Shields are marked " L " and “ R ”, the '' L '' fits glasses left leg, the " R " fits glasses right leg.
